<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>About Us</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .content-container {
      margin: 0;
      margin-top: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .image-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      position: relative;
    }

    .image-section img {
      width: 90%;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeDown 1.5s ease forwards;
      animation-delay: 0.5s;
    }

    @keyframes fadeDown {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-20px);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    /* Change Background Color of Content Section */
    .content-section {
      padding: 20px 200px;
      margin-top: 0px;
      text-align: left;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      background-color: none; /* Light gray background color */
      border-radius: 10px; /* Optional: rounded corners */
    }

    /* Ribbon Animation */
    .ribbon-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .ribbon {
      position: relative;
      padding: 10px 30px;
      background-color: #DF9EB2;
      color: white;
      font-size: 2em;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: center;
      clip-path: polygon(10% 0, 90% 0, 100% 50%, 90% 100%, 10% 100%, 0 50%);
    }

    /* Change Background Color of Text Container */
    .text-container {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: white; /* Soft pink background color */
      border-radius: 8px; /* Optional: rounded corners */
    }

    .text-container p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin: 0;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .read-more {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      
    }

    .btn-get-started {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: transparent;
      color: #617952;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 2px solid #617952;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 50px;
      width: 150px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      margin: 20px auto;
      display: block;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .btn-get-started:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      background-color: #FDEDF1;
      color: #617952;
      box-shadow: 0px 6px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
  </style>
  <script>
    function toggleReadMore() {
      const readMoreContent = document.getElementById('read-more-content');
      const readMoreButton = document.getElementById('read-more-button');
      if (readMoreContent.style.display === 'none') {
        readMoreContent.style.display = 'block';
        readMoreButton.innerText = 'Read Less';
      } else {
        readMoreContent.style.display = 'none';
        readMoreButton.innerText = 'Read More';
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body>

<div class="content-container">
  <!-- Image Section -->
  <div class="image-section">
    <img src="<%= asset_path('about-page.png') %>" alt="Story Image">
  </div>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <div class="content-section">
    <!-- Animated Ribbon Title -->
    <div class="ribbon-container">
      <div class="ribbon">About Us</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text Container -->
    <div class="text-container">
      <p>
        AIT Match is a unique platform designed exclusively for the students of the Asian Institute of Technology (AIT). 
        With AIT's diverse and graduate-focused community, connecting with peers who share similar academic interests and backgrounds 
        can be challenging. AIT Match aims to bridge this gap by fostering meaningful connections within the AIT student body, 
        enhancing both social and academic engagement.
      </p>
      <button id="read-more-button" class="btn-get-started" onclick="toggleReadMore()">Read More</button>
      
      <div id="read-more-content" class="read-more">
        <p>
          Our platform offers a customized matching system that allows students to connect based on their academic programs, schools, 
          majors, interests, and upcoming campus events. Whether you're looking to form study groups, collaborate on academic projects, 
          or build lasting friendships, AIT Match helps you find like-minded peers. Additionally, for those interested in romantic connections, 
          AIT Match provides a trusted environment to explore relationships within the AIT community, ensuring a balanced mix of social, academic, 
          and romantic interactions.
        </p><br>
        <p>
          AIT Match is specifically made for the needs of university students, combining social networking, academic collaboration, 
          and romantic possibilities in one space. It is the ideal platform for AIT students seeking a community that supports both their personal 
          and academic journeys. Our goal is to create an inclusive and vibrant community where students can connect, collaborate, and growâ€”both 
          academically and personally.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>